"...we have no such custom...

830
01:33:59,035 --> 01:34:01,299
"...neither the Churches of God.

831
01:34:01,370 --> 01:34:04,965
"Now in this that I declare
unto you I praise you not...

832
01:34:05,041 --> 01:34:07,305
"...that ye come together
not for the better...

833
01:34:07,376 --> 01:34:08,673
"...but for the worse."

