843
01:37:14,897 --> 01:37:18,663
They are coming! The
Tatars are coming, Prince!

844
01:38:07,383 --> 01:38:10,147
Hey, Prince! Is this your ford?

845
01:38:11,053 --> 01:38:15,285
It has been raining, and
everything is flooded. Follow us.

846
01:38:45,254 --> 01:38:48,121
We were just going to leave.
We expected you yesterday.

847
01:38:48,924 --> 01:38:53,827
I couldn't resist attacking
a small town on my way.

848
01:38:53,963 --> 01:38:54,952
I am sorry I am late.

849
01:38:55,130 --> 01:38:57,997
Never mind. Let's go. It will be
shallow to the left. Keep to the left.

850
01:39:02,771 --> 01:39:04,966
This isn't a trap?

851
01:39:05,341 --> 01:39:07,332
Believe me, Vladimir is deserted.

852
01:39:07,476 --> 01:39:10,411
My brother, the Grand
Prince, is in Lithuania.

853
01:39:10,579 --> 01:39:12,604
Here is the town, behind that forest.

854
01:39:13,249 --> 01:39:17,015
They say the Prince has a
son, but you want the throne.

855
01:39:18,554 --> 01:39:19,919
We'll see.

856
01:39:21,323 --> 01:39:24,292
I see you want the
throne. I understand.

857
01:39:30,032 --> 01:39:31,624
You were told to keep left.

858
01:39:37,806 --> 01:39:38,966
Grab this!

859
01:41:13,736 --> 01:41:16,227
Come on, Prince! Don't lag behind!

860
01:41:28,183 --> 01:41:29,741
Strong is your love for your brother.

861
01:41:30,119 --> 01:41:31,780
This is our destiny.

862
01:41:32,788 --> 01:41:34,551
When were you last
reconciled with him?

863
01:41:34,957 --> 01:41:38,358
I never was. The
Metropolitan summoned us...

864
01:41:40,162 --> 01:41:42,630
...and made us kiss the cross
and swear to live in harmony.

865
01:41:42,698 --> 01:41:43,687
What are you saying?

866
01:41:43,766 --> 01:41:45,700
The Metropolitan
summoned us to kiss the cross.

867
01:41:45,768 --> 01:41:47,929
- When?
- Last winter.

868
01:42:42,691 --> 01:42:45,023
Vladimir is a beautiful town.

869
01:42:45,093 --> 01:42:46,219
Do you like it?

870
01:42:56,171 --> 01:42:57,570
Let's go.

871
01:43:41,850 --> 01:43:45,684
Forward! You dog,
stay close, or I'll kill you!

872
01:43:47,322 --> 01:43:50,723
Keep close to the
Prince! To the gates!

873
01:44:43,679 --> 01:44:45,408
Tatars!

874
01:44:46,181 --> 01:44:48,149
Run away!

875
01:45:55,817 --> 01:45:57,808
What is going on?

876
01:47:26,908 --> 01:47:29,240
The Grand Prince is coming.

877
01:47:40,489 --> 01:47:42,013
The brother has arrived.